        How Real Estate Agents Get Paid in Queensland: Commission, Fees and What Sellers Need to Understand
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Queensland has no regulated commission rate. Here is a plain-English breakdown of how agent commission works, what you should negotiate, and where sellers commonly get caught out.
      </p>
